description: Exquisite brick & beam corner loft in Boston’s vibrant Seaport, fully renovated in 2022 with timeless charm and modern luxury. Soaring 12’ ceilings and oversized windows flood the space with natural light, highlighting exposed brick and rich hardwood floors. The expansive 31’ x 14’ great room provides a dramatic backdrop for entertaining or tailoring to your lifestyle with ease. A chef’s kitchen shines with stainless appliances, granite counters, custom cabinetry, and stylish barn doors. The king-sized primary suite boasts an ensuite bath, dual walk-ins, and abundant storage, complemented by a spacious second bedroom and new full bath. Deeded parking ensures effortless living, while the coveted location between Congress St. and Seaport Blvd places you steps from Boston’s finest dining, shopping, nightlife, and cultural attractions. A truly rare opportunity to own a stunning residence in one of the city’s most desirable neighborhoods.
